(175, 'sjc14', '软件/互联网开发/系统集成', '软件工程师', 'IOS Developer', '6000', '15000', '2', '193', 'Responsibilities\r\n1、Design and build advanced applications for the Android or iOS platform\r\n2、Collaborate with cross-functional teams to design, develop and ship new features.\r\n3、Unit-test code for robustness, including edge cases, usability, and general reliability.\r\n4、Work on bug fixing and improving application performance.\r\nRequirements\r\n1、BS/MS degree in Computer Science, Engineering or a related subject\r\nSolid Java or object-c programing skill is a MUST.\r\n2、2+ years of software development experience\r\n3、1+ years of Android or iOS development \r\n4、Experience with Android/iOS SDK\r\n5、Experience working with remote data via REST and JSON\r\n6、Solid understanding of the full mobile development life cycle.'),
(176, 'sjc14', 'IT质量管理/测试/配置管理', '软件测试', 'QA', '4000', '6000', '7', '194', '1. 5 + years of QA experience. \r\n2. Good at test cases creation/execution according to customer requirements. \r\n3. Familiar with kinds of software test modes and test tools. \r\n4. Familiar with Windows OS platforms, i.e. Windows 2008, Windows 2012, Win7, Win8. \r\n5. Good Spoken English to communicate with others. \r\n6. Have experience on LDAP and Email servers configuration. \r\n7. Familiar with SQL Server 2008/2012 installation, configuration, database creation/Restore and SQL language. \r\n8. Better to have experience on QTP or Selenium automation.'),
(177, 'sjc14', 'IT质量管理/测试/配置管理', '软件测试', 'Linux Shell QE', '4000', '6000', '7', '195', 'Responsibilities\r\nDevelop detailed automated tests from test plans, engineering discussions and functional specifications.\r\nCreate, maintain and extend the automated test infrastructure\r\nTroubleshoot test case and test harness infrastructure failures\r\nAnalyze automation test run results and report bugs\r\nSkills and Experience\r\nAbility to translate software system architectures into an integrated approach to software test\r\nExperience as developer/programmer in a software engineering environment.\r\nExperience with QA automation tools, scripting languages(shell), and programming languages (flex/Java/c/c++)\r\nExperience in Linux/Unix administration, knowledge about TET, file system, storage, web services, or Linux kernel is desirable\r\nAbility to set priorities, meet deadlines, and work independently\r\nSolid written English communication skills\r\nKnowledge about ESX, vSphere SDK is desirable'),
(178, 'sjc14', 'IT质量管理/测试/配置管理', '软件测试', 'Senior Automation Tester', '4000', '6000', '4', '196', '1. Solid Object-Oriented Programming sense and hands-on experience in either C# or Java or any other languages.\r\n2. Hands-on experience in Selenium WebDriver is a must, able to encapsulate/upgrade the primitive Selenium APIs.\r\n3. Good verbal and written English capability is a must, able to talk with native English speakers over phone.\r\n4. At least 3 year of software functional testing experience.'),
(179, 'sjc14', 'IT质量管理/测试/配置管理', '软件测试', 'Application QE', '4000', '6000', '7', '197', '1. 5+ years of functional testing experience\r\n2. Capable to be a quick learner to new business (GUI management console for cloud backup & restore)\r\n3. Decent capability and experience on requirement/functional spec digestion (Ruby-on-Rails web application test experience is a big plus)\r\n4. Can work on its own to design decent test cases, execute test & report status/issues (Can drive issues to solution is a big plus)\r\n5. Decent communication skill with peers, dev counterparts, leads/mgrs\r\n6. Teamwork spirit and team player\r\n7. Web automated test experience is a big plus\r\n8. Any coding skill is a plus (Prefer Ruby)\r\n9. Good communication skills (written and verbal) in both English and Mandarin\r\nEducation and Experience:\r\n1. 3-8 years’ experience in Software QA Area\r\n2. BS or equivalent in Computer Science or Engineering'),
(180, 'sjc14', 'IT质量管理/测试/配置管理', '软件测试', 'Linux shell QA', '4000', '6000', '4', '198', 'Responsibilities\r\n1. Develop detailed automated tests from test plans, engineering discussions and functional specifications.\r\n2. Create, maintain and extend the automated test infrastructure\r\n3. Troubleshoot test case and test harness infrastructure failures\r\n4. Analyze automation test run results and report bugs\r\nSkills and Experience\r\n1. Ability to translate software system architectures into an integrated approach to software test\r\n2. Experience as developer/programmer in a software engineering environment.\r\n3. Experience with QA automation tools, scripting languages(shell), and programming languages (flex/Java/c/c++)\r\n4. Experience in Linux/Unix administration, knowledge about TET, file system, storage, web services, or Linux kernel is desirable\r\n5. Ability to set priorities, meet deadlines, and work independently\r\n6. Solid written English communication skills\r\n7. Knowledge about ESX, vSphere SDK is desirable'),
(181, 'sjc14', '软件/互联网开发/系统集成', '高级软件工程师', 'Senior Web Software Engineer', '10000', '20000', '4', '199', 'For Web Software Engineer, here''s a list of "MUST" requirements:\r\n1. HTML, CSS, Javascript\r\n2. Ruby or Java\r\n3. RDBMS SQL'),
(182, 'sjc14', '软件/互联网开发/系统集成', '高级软件工程师', 'Senior Java Engineer', '10000', '20000', '4', '200', 'Software development, responsible for coding, testing and documentation activities. Develop, unit test, document, and deploy J2EE software system.\r\n1. More than 3 years IT experience and at least 2 years of J2EE development experience.\r\n2. Familiar with Core Java.\r\n3. Familiar with Design Pattern.\r\n4. Familiar with SQL server/Oracle.\r\n5. Familiar to UML and other mainstream development and design tools.\r\n6. Good English skill.\r\n7. Give priority to have experience of product maintenance or product secondary development.\r\n8. Passion for work, good team player'),
(183, 'sjc14', '软件/互联网开发/系统集成', '高级软件工程师', 'Senior PHP Engineer', '10000', '20000', '4', '201', '1. 计算机或相关专业,3年以上工作经验； \r\n2. 有互联网领域三年以上设计、开发实现工作经验； \r\n3. 熟练掌握PHP+MySQL环境的Web应用开发，熟练掌握MySQL数据库设计开发； \r\n4. 熟悉ThinkPHP开发框架及相关衍生产品； \r\n5. 熟悉JAVASCRIPT、HTML、CSS，熟悉面向对象的开发方式； \r\n6. 熟悉LINUX操作系统的常用命令操作和应用系统部署、运行维护； \r\n7. 能自主完成模块开发，有与后台系统集成的经验者优先； \r\n8. 具备良好的代码编程习惯、较强的文档编写能力、学习能力和沟通能力； \r\n9. 责任心强，踏实好学，具备良好的职业素养及团队合作精神。'),
(184, 'sjc14', '软件/互联网开发/系统集成', '高级软件工程师', 'Senior .Net Engineer', '10000', '20000', '7', '202', '职位描述:\r\n1. 能够对项目进行深入的需求分析，评估开发时间，制定开发计划；；\r\n2. 根据开发进度和任务分配，按时按质完成相应模块软件的设计、开发、编程任务；\r\n3. 编写模块详细设计文档、解决方案；\r\n4. 参与软件开发技术和规范及标准流程的改进；\r\n5. 参与软件系统的设计和分析；\r\n6. 能够带领初，中级程序员进行项目开发。\r\n任职要求：\r\n1. 计算机及相关专业毕业，或具有同等工作经历经验，本科以上学历；\r\n2. 5年以上相关软件开发工作经验，具备系统架构、系统设计的能力；\r\n3. 了解敏捷思想；\r\n4. 熟练掌握ASP.NET/ C#、XML、WCF、HTML、JavaScript、 jQuery、CSS等相关技术\r\n5. 熟练掌握SQL Server数据库设计及SQL脚本；\r\n6. 有良好的工作态度、学习习惯及团队合作能力，能够独立承担工作压力，要有较强的分析和解决问题的能力；\r\n7. 有电力行业软件和大型项目开发经验者优先；'),
(185, 'sjc14', '软件/互联网开发/系统集成', '软件工程师', 'C++ Developer', '6000', '15000', '4', '203', '1. Good team worker with high cooperative spirit.\r\n2. Strong capable of problem solving and communication.\r\n3. Skilled in C/C++.\r\n4. Highly proficient in Windows environment and proficient with Visual Studio.\r\n5. COM/ATL knowledge.\r\n6. Multi-thread and inter-process communication knowledge.\r\n7. Experience with SQL Server (or other Database).\r\n8. Scripting skills in one common language (Python, Perl or Tcl) will be preferred.\r\n9. Web development especially for client side will be preferred.'),
(186, 'sjc14', '软件/互联网开发/系统集成', 'WEB前端开发', 'Web Developer', '4000', '6000', '7', '204', '1. Feel comfort and has ability to work with various web platforms and languages Ruby/C++/Java, Ruby on Rails are preferred\r\n2. Has project experience with large scale, multiple layer and big data management backend systems\r\n3. Familiar with OO concepts, has experience with common design patterns\r\n4. Familiar with Linux development environment, Ubuntu/Debian is preferred\r\n5. Knowledge of web services implementation techniques such as REST or SOAP\r\n6. Expertise with traditional RDBMS SQL development including PostgreSQL/Oralce/MySQL/SQLite, NOSQL experience is preferred, such as MongoDB/CouchDB/Cassandra/Redis\r\n7. Demonstrated strong motivation and ability to meet milestones and deadlines for commercial software products.\r\n8. Ability to work in a fast paced environment and learn new things quickly\r\n9. Good communication skill in both English and Mandarin\r\nEducation and Experience:\r\n1. About 3~8 years’ experience in web system development\r\n2. BS or equivalent in Computer Science or Engineering'),
(187, 'sjc14', '软件/互联网开发/系统集成', '高级软件工程师', 'Senior .Net Tech Lead', '10000', '20000', '7', '205', 'Skills and Experience: \r\n1. 6+ years .NET development experience \r\n2. Experience in .NET, C# \r\n3. Experience with WCF \r\n4. Experience with MVVM framework \r\n5. Experience with database design such as SQL Server / Oracle \r\n6. Experience with unit test framework \r\n7. Good communication skills (written English) \r\n8. Experience of Agile development processes an advantage \r\n9. Very strong development skills are essential. \r\n\r\nDuties and Responsibilities: \r\n1. Responsibility for the design and development of .net Web application, collaborating with engineers, test engineers and product stakeholders within an Agile environment. \r\n2. Responsible for code reviews and technical quality standards within the project team \r\n3. Carry out unit tests to ensure a high quality deliverable.'),
(188, 'sjc14', '软件/互联网开发/系统集成', '高级软件工程师', 'Senior Java Engineer', '10000', '20000', '2', '206', '1. Four years or more experience in Java software design and development;\r\n2. Solid technology base of Java developing, design patterns, data structure, database;\r\n3. Experience in platform architecture designing, SOA architecture technology, be familiar with SOAP, REST etc.;\r\n4. Good understanding to the core technology of J2EE and common design patterns; be familiar with the database postgreSQL as a plus;\r\n5. Familiar with network programming, understanding to TCP/IP as a plus;\r\n6. Familiar with log4j, the experience of generating word, PDF format files as a plus;\r\n7. Responsible, good teamwork spirit and communication skills, be able to work independently;'),
(189, 'sjc14', '软件/互联网开发/系统集成', '高级软件工程师', '.Net Engineer', '10000', '20000', '2', '207', '职位描述:\r\n1. 按软件开发流程和生命周期进行软件开发\r\n2. 开发大型Web应用系统/大型网站等\r\n3. 根据项目要求，完成软件项目的可行性与需求分析\r\n4. 编写实现代码、进行单元测试\r\n5. 按要求编写开发设计文档\r\n \r\n任职要求：\r\n1. 计算机及相关专业毕业，或具有同等工作经历经验，本科以上学历；\r\n2. 2年以上.NET平台下WEB开发经验；\r\n3. 熟练掌握ASP.NET/ C#、HTML、JavaScript、 jQuery、CSS等相关技术\r\n4. 具有一定数据库知识，熟悉SQL Server数据库；\r\n5. 具有较强的逻辑思维，良好的编程风格，一定的面向对象编程、设计模式基础\r\n6. 具有良好的沟通能力和团队合作精神'),
(190, 'sjc14', '软件/互联网开发/系统集成', '高级软件工程师', 'Windows/Linux C++ App Developer', '10000', '20000', '4', '208', '1. Proficient with Visual Studio, or Linux GCC/GDB,\r\n2. HTTP knowledge, REST API preferred\r\n3. Multiple threading and inter-process communication knowledge is a big plus\r\n4. Proficient with Bash/Python/Perl/Ruby is a big plus for Linux developers\r\n5. Familiar with Boost C++ framework, Git source control and continuous integration tool and process\r\n6. Cloud storage or file backup/sync project experience is beneficial\r\n7. Good communication skill in both English and Mandarin'),
(191, 'sjc14', '软件/互联网开发/系统集成', '高级软件工程师', 'Senior .Net Engineer', '10000', '20000', '4', '209', '1. 6~8 year software development experiences.\r\n2. 4 years web development experiences.\r\n3. Be familiar with C#, asp.net, asp.net MVC.\r\n4. Be familiar with Ajax, JavaScript, HTML/DHTML, CSS. Experiences in Ext JS, jQuery is preferred.\r\n5. Be familiar with Web Service, WCF.\r\n6. Has experiences in database designing and modeling, be familiar with relational databases like MS SQL Server, Oracle.\r\n7. Has architecture design experiences, be familiar with object-oriented design, design patterns.\r\n8. Good oral English is must.'),
(192, 'sjc14', '软件/互联网开发/系统集成', '高级软件工程师', 'Linux Ruby(or Python, Perl) Engineer', '10000', '20000', '4', '210', '1. Experience with Unix/Linux/ system concepts\r\n2. Experience with test automation skill - Ruby, Python, Perl\r\n3. Good communication skills (both verbal and written)\r\n4. 3+ years of Functional testing experience');
